sdg_83_title: Promote policies to support job creation and growing enterprises
sdg_83_subtitle: Promote policies to support productivity, decent job creation and entrepreneurship
sdg_83_paragraph_1: These actions reflect Cambodia's emphasis on inclusive economic diversification, SME support, and climate resilience.
sdg_83_paragraph_2: Supporting rural women entrepreneurs, energy management improvements, and 3R strategies can unlock jobs and growth.
